      "author": "player-Muteki",
      "description": "## Changed\n- Extracted business/session/streaming logic from \\CopsidianView\\ into new \\CopsidianViewController\\ class\n- View now handles only DOM creation, UI event binding, and Obsidian lifecycle hooks\n- Controller owns connection management, session lifecycle, message sending, toolbar sync, and state\n- View delegates all operations to controller via \\ControllerDeps\\ and \\ControllerCallbacks\\ interfaces\n- Added 32 unit tests for controller methods\n\n## What's Changed\n* feat: Expand MCP server types and support terminal tool results by @player-Muteki in https://github.com/player-Muteki/copsidian/pull/22\n* feat: implement requestWithFallback in AcpClient by @player-Muteki in https://github.com/player-Muteki/copsidian/pull/21\n* feat(ui): drive UI from agentCapabilities (v0.0.24) by @player-Muteki in https://github.com/player-Muteki/copsidian/pull/24\n* feat(tooling): eslint, prettier, gitignore, ACP matrix (v0.0.25) by @player-Muteki in https://github.com/player-Muteki/copsidian/pull/27\n* feat: introduce SessionUpdateNormalizer for client state machine by @player-Muteki in https://github.com/player-Muteki/copsidian/pull/23\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/player-Muteki/copsidian/compare/v0.0.21...v0.0.28",
